@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Researcher Logs In

actor Researcher
participant "Frontend/UI" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
database "Database \n (Firebase)" as DB

Researcher -> UI: Open 'Login' page
Researcher -> UI: Fill login form and submit
UI -> API: POST /auth/login
API -> DB: Verify Researcher credentials
DB --> API: Success/Failure response
API --> UI: Return result (success/failure)
UI --> Researcher: Show confirmation or error

@enduml
